### AidFlow API — Wallets endpoints
# REST Client extension: click 'Send Request' above each block

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api/v1
@token = REPLACE_WITH_JWT_TOKEN

### List wallets (501 in Sprint 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/wallets
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get wallet by ID (501 in Sprint 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/wallets/WALLET_ID
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get wallet balance (501 in Sprint 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/wallets/WALLET_ID/balance
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get wallet ledger (501 in Sprint 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/wallets/WALLET_ID/ledger
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
